  | equals ƒink:
    ·fn
      fn ·ƒcaps_57, ·ƒctx_40, ·ƒret_6, ·a_2, ·b_3: ·op_plus ·ƒctx_40, ·a_2, ·b_3, ·ƒret_6
      fn ·v_60:
